Relevant backend surfaces:

- Shop admin logic: `backend/laravel/app/Http/Controllers/Api/AdminController.php`
- Shop player logic: `backend/laravel/app/Http/Controllers/Api/ShopController.php`
- Nation/player dashboard data: `backend/laravel/app/Http/Controllers/Api/MeController.php`
- Other nation/admin nation editing: `backend/laravel/app/Http/Controllers/Api/NationController.php` and `backend/laravel/app/Http/Controllers/Api/AdminController.php`

